transforms.code:
WeekEnd = self.params.WeekEndDate
	date = value
	DateList = []
	while date != WeekEnd:
		formated_date = system.date.format(date,'yyyy-MM-dd')
		DateList.append(formated_date)
		date = system.date.addDays(date, 1)
	DateList.append(system.date.format(WeekEnd,'yyyy-MM-dd'))
	return DateList
